data.title: List of decommissioned United States Marine Corps aircraft squadrons
data.meta_description: While other nations have Marines who are aviators, only the United States Marine Corps has its own dedicated aviation arm. Most squadrons have changed names and designations many times over the years so they are listed by their final designation.
